divs: Sighting DetailsTraveling west on the I-10 just North of Palm Springs witnessed a very bright Blu-Green Ball of light which seemed to be just above San Jacinto Mountain which borders Palm Springs, shortly after there was a bright white light maybe an impact really cannot say. Continued to travel west on the I-10 West while looking up the San Jacinto Mountain from its NW side there seemed to be a plume did not notice any clouds in the area, my boyfriend phoned KESQ-News and spoke to someone that confirmed something to the same sighting over the scanner, please check this out.
